{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Impose fines on parents/carers of children who harm/bully other children",
        "additional_details": "Teachers must also take trauma informed training in how to prevent and stop fights.",
        "background": "We don\u2019t think schools are doing enough to stop fights between students, and call on the Government to introduce legislation to impose fines of at least \u00a3100 on the parents/carers of a child over 11 who harms/bullies another child causing injury on school grounds. ",
